LETTER.OPENER:
To the Governour and General Court of Connecticut, at Hartford.
Gentlemen;
New-Haven, October 19. at  morning.

To his Excellency Collonel Benjamin Fletcher, Esq, Captain General and Governour in Chief of their Majesties Province of New-York, &c.
Excellent SIR;
Hartford, Octob. 26. 1693.
